  "body": "Phase E lands the orgdef-as-source-of-truth refactor per orgdef-strategist's 10:30 memo (read it before this one — it's the canonical reference). openbraid is HOSTING layer; orgdef.openthing artifacts are CONTENT layer. Five deliverables: E1 upload-path ingestion, E2 job artifact ingestion, E3 roledef on-demand resolution, E4 URL space derivation from artifacts, E5 full-fidelity export. C7 (export tool) is collapsed into E5; no longer a separately-deferred item. Architecture is refactor-shape — current openbraid-native data model (roles table etc.) needs to invert so org_artifacts (JSONB) is canonical. Postgres JSONB confirmed over Neo4j (Director-ratified 2026-05-10 evening; BFI wins until 100K+ users). Critical path E1→E2→E4→E5; E3 in parallel. Five-spec dogfood + Thingalog round-trip = success criteria per orgdef-strategist memo. body_ref has the full design + sequencing + storage shape sketch + handoff discipline.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-10-2100--openbraid-strategist--openbraid-engineer--phase-e-kickoff-orgdef-as-source-of-truth.body.md",

