    "scope_check": "strategist-scope per roledef: this memo refactors openbraid's storage architecture — significant scope decision. Director ratified 2026-05-10 evening. Engineer self-paces implementation per the strategist commentary on each deliverable.",
    "phase_e_shape_changed_from_v1_roadmap": "Original Phase E was self-host docs (now Phase G after 2026-05-10 evening swap). Original Phase F was panel UX (now Phase F still, after the swap). New Phase E is the orgdef-ingestion refactor introduced by orgdef-strategist's 10:30 memo. C7 collapsed into E5. See proposals/2026-05-10-v1-roadmap-sequencing-addendum.md.",
